---
import Title from "./Title.astro";
import Subtitle from "./Subtitle.astro";
---

<section id="portfolio" class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        <!-- Section header with CTA -->
        <div class="products-header flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end md:justify-between gap-6 mb-16">
            <div class="max-w-2xl">
                <Title>Инновационные проекты, меняющие жизни</Title>
                <Subtitle>
                    От идеи до реализации — мы создаем технологические решения для корпоративных и государственных клиентов.
                </Subtitle>
            </div>
            <a href="#contacts" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#0052CC] to-[#4C9AFF] text-white font-semibold rounded-md shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-0.5 whitespace-nowrap relative">
                <!-- Decorative dashed borders -->
                <span class="absolute -left-2 top-2 bottom-2 border-l-2 border-dashed border-[#4C9AFF]/40"></span>
                <span class="absolute -right-2 top-2 bottom-2 border-r-2 border-dashed border-[#4C9AFF]/40"></span>
                Начать проект
            </a>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Stepped 3-card layout -->
        <div class="relative bg-gray-100 rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-10 lg:p-12">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 lg:gap-0 items-center">
                <!-- Left card (shorter) -->
                <div class="product-card group bg-white rounded-2xl md:rounded-r-none shadow-lg overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 md:my-8">
                    <div class="p-8 md:p-8 lg:p-10 flex flex-col h-full">
                        <div class="inline-block mb-4">
                            <div class="rounded-lg text-sm font-medium text-red-600 px-4 py-2 bg-red-50 border border-red-200">
                                Чрезвычайные ситуации
                            </div>    
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold leading-tight mb-3 text-gray-900 group-hover:text-red-600 transition-colors">
                            ЧС Алматы
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-base text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                            Ваш надежный спутник безопасности в любой ситуации.
                        </p>
                        <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-2 mt-auto">
                            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                                </svg>
                                <span>Критические уведомления</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                                </svg>
                                <span>SOS-система с геолокацией</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                                </svg>
                                <span>Офлайн-навигация</span>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                        <a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center font-semibold text-red-600 hover:text-red-700 transition-colors mt-6">
                            <span class="mr-1 text-lg">▸</span>
                            <span>Подробнее</span>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Center card (taller, elevated) -->
                <div class="product-card central-card group bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-2xl overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 relative z-10 md:-my-4">
                    <div class="h-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#0052CC] to-[#4C9AFF]"></div>
                    <div class="p-8 md:p-8 lg:p-10 flex flex-col h-full">
                        <div class="inline-block mb-4">
                            <div class="rounded-lg text-sm font-medium text-blue-600 px-4 py-2 bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200">
                                Обучение
                            </div>    
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold leading-tight mb-3 text-gray-900 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">
                            Quick AI
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-base text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                            Революционное AI-решение для эффективного обучения через видеоконтент.
                        </p>
                        <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-2 mt-auto">
                            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                                </svg>
                                <span>Обработка видео любой продолжительности</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                                </svg>
                                <span>Генерация структурированных конспектов</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                                </svg>
                                <span>Персонализированные тесты</span>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                        <a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center font-semibold text-[#0052CC] hover:text-[#4C9AFF] transition-colors mt-6">
                            <span class="mr-1 text-lg">▸</span>
                            <span>Подробнее</span>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Right card (shorter) -->
                <div class="product-card group bg-white rounded-2xl md:rounded-l-none shadow-lg overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 md:my-8">
                    <div class="p-8 md:p-8 lg:p-10 flex flex-col h-full">
                        <div class="inline-block mb-4">
                            <div class="rounded-lg text-sm font-medium text-green-700 px-4 py-2 bg-green-50 border border-green-200">
                                Образование
                            </div>    
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold leading-tight mb-3 text-gray-900 group-hover:text-green-600 transition-colors">
                            Azbuka 4D
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-base text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                            Дополненная реальность для изучения техники безопасности.
                        </p>
                        <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-2 mt-auto">
                            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                                </svg>
                                <span>Фотореалистичные 3D-модели</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                                </svg>
                                <span>Виртуальные тренажеры</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                                </svg>
                                <span>Обучение работе с оборудованием</span>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                        <a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center font-semibold text-green-600 hover:text-green-700 transition-colors mt-6">
                            <span class="mr-1 text-lg">▸</span>
                            <span>Подробнее</span>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .product-card {
        transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    }
    .product-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-4px);
    }
    .central-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-8px);
    }
</style>
